name: NAIL PERP
description: Nail Prep - dehydrates natural nails and removes natural oils, increasing adhesion and duration for nail polishes, acrylic and gel systems. Apply before XTRABOND (primer).

name: UV FINISH GEL
description: UV FINISH GEL is clear thin viscosity gel with an ultrashine finish that has no sticky residues after UV or LED lamp cures. It is used for any artificial enhancement: gels, acrylic or wraps. Artificial nail use only.

name: GLASS FINISH LED/UV GEL
description: This Glass Finish is a soak-off clear UV-LED Gel which can be used over natural nails or any enhancements. It won't leave any sticky residue after curing, therefore there is no need to clean it afterwards.
